head
  meta(charset='UTF-8')
  link(rel='stylesheet' href='../layouts/AddStyle.css')
  title Add Review
script#script(src='../content/addReviewFunctionality.js' onload='init()' defer='')
h1(title = movieTitle )#title Enter Movie Review for: !{movieTitle}
|     There are two methods to add a review to a movie.
br
br
|     1) simply give the movie a score out of 10
br
br
